goBastion Templates Extension

Provides syntax highlighting for goBastion templates.

Features

Highlights go:: logic lines (embedding Go syntax).

Highlights ::end closing tags.

Highlights @variable and @expression(...) echoes.

Full HTML support as the base language.

Development & Installation

1. Run in Debug Mode

Open this folder in VS Code.

Press F5 to launch a new Extension Development Host window.

Open the examples/home.gb.html file to test.

2. Package & Install (.vsix)

Prerequisite: Install vsce (npm install -g @vscode/vsce).

Run:

vsce package


This generates a .vsix file.

Install via command palette: Extensions: Install from VSIX...
